00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:32.800
It was traditionally used as anesthesia in surgery.
这种药传统上是用于手术中的麻醉剂。

168
00:08:33.360 --> 00:08:35.016
But unlike those other drugs,
不像其他的药物，

