00:09:11.400 --> 00:09:12.816
And we were just piloting.
我们只是在试验，

184
00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:15.096
So we would give an injection to mice,
所以我们会给老鼠注射

185
00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:16.416
