00:09:29.280 --> 00:09:30.800
So we could have stopped there.
所以我们本应该停止。

192
00:09:31.360 --> 00:09:34.256
But I have run this model of depression for years,
但是我做这个抑郁试验多年，

193
00:09:34.280 --> 00:09:36.176
and the data just looked kind of weird.
收集到的数据有些怪。

