which is impossible.
不可思议。

220
00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:43.800
So we could have just stopped there,
我们本可以就此打住，

221
00:10:44.600 --> 00:10:48.896
but Christine had also used Calypsol before as anesthesia,
但是Christine曾经使用过Calypsol 做为麻醉药物，

