00:11:03.480 --> 00:11:06.016
So we did what you do in science when you're not sure,
于是我们做了在科学上当你疑惑的时候该做的事，

231
00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:07.240
and we ran it again.
再次试验。

232
00:11:08.280 --> 00:11:11.296
And I remember being in the animal room,
我记得在动物房

